title: Priority One Equipment Financing Announces New Website Launch
text:
Priority One Equipment Financing Announces New Website Launch October 15, 2015, 06:25 AM Related: Priority One Financial Services 
Priority One Financial Services has announced the launch of its new website for their equipment financing services division.The new website provides an extensive list of the commercial vehicles and equipment that can be financed, such as company trucks, rental boats and RVs, buses, trailers, repair lifts, forklifts and more plus easy step-by-step instructions on how the financing process works.According to Jared Zimlin, Business Development Director of Priority One, “We are excited about our new website launch so we can provide more information and enhanced contact points for dealers and customers.”Other website features include: How to contact Priority One Company history and employee profiles 
The new website can be accessed at www.p1fs.com/commercial . Today's Other News
